oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Carl Smith Fact Sheet: Version 1 (masking sheet)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Offset printing; Smith, Carl, 1927-2010;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative framed by a masking sheet advertising facts about Carl Smith including his birth place; songs recorded; albums recorded; movies, radio, and television shows he appeared on; record label; awards; countries visited; and hobbies. The negative appears to be the first version of the fact sheet, as some information is removed in version two.
